[I] Ball bouncing game

[T] KBounce is a single player arcade game with the elements of puzzle. It is
[T] played on a field, surrounded by wall, with two or more balls that move
[T] about in the field bouncing off of walls.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kbounce/

